{"article_id":"00eP4XD3VdMmHITE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Is Maine Republican Sen. Susan Collins being bribed","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to vote against Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh ?","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"That ' s what she and others are saying .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"The conservative-leaning news site Newsmax reported on Monday","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"that a prominent Republican elections lawyer is calling for an investigation into what it described as a more than $ 1 million \" threat \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"hanging over Collins ' s head ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"depending on her vote on Kavanaugh .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"In a statement to Newsmax , Collins said","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"she believed","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"there was an attempt to \" bribe \" her vote","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"and said","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"she wouldn ' t be the target of \" quid pro quo fundraising . \"","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"But no one is actually trying to give Collins money","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"to vote against Kavanaugh .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Instead , what Newsmax and Collins are referring to is a crowdfunding campaign","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"run on the progressive political crowdfunding platform Crowdpac .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Launched by ALS patient and activist Ady Barkan , the grassroots community action organization Maine People ' s Alliance , and the activist and watchdog group Mainers for Accountable Leadership ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the campaign is meant to encourage Collins to vote against Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"It ' s raised $ 1.1 million so far ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"but that money will never go to Collins .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The proposition :","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"If Collins votes against Kavanaugh ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"donors","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"who have pledged to the campaign","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"won ' t be charged .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"If she votes for him ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"the funds","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"raised","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"will go to her Democratic opponent","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"when she is up for reelection in 2020 .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"I may be losing my voice ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"but I can still send a message ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and I have one for @ SenatorCollins :","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"If you vote for Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"we will fund your future opponent for 2020 .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Vote NO","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and # StopKavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"# BeAHero","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Pledge $ 20.20 to this campaign","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and share it :","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"https : //t.co/4HPtATVrXc","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"pic.twitter.com/ZkdI3u57yY","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"- Ady Barkan","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"( @ AdyBarkan )","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"August 16 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Collins and Alaska ' s Sen. Lisa Murkowski are considered to be the two key votes on Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"who will determine","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"whether he is confirmed as a justice of the US Supreme Court .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Both women are in favor of abortion rights ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"and progressives have been pushing them fiercely to oppose Kavanaugh ' s nomination","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"because of concerns over his stance on Roe v. Wade and the possibility","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that he might vote to overturn or chip away at the landmark case .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Kavanaugh and Collins met in August ,","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"and she said","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"he told her","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that the matter was \" settled law , \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"even though ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"as ' s Anna North pointed out ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"during his confirmation hearing last week , Kavanaugh largely danced around","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"giving a straight answer on the issue .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"There ' s some back-and-forth over the legality of the crowdfunding campaign","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"At issue here is whether Collins is being , essentially , paid for her vote .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"As mentioned ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"the crowdfunding campaign isn ' t promising a donation to her campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"but","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"if she votes no ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"it would give money to her eventual opponent .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"T.J. Adams-Falconer , a spokesperson for Crowdpac , told Newsmax","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that the platform had been \" thoroughly vetted \" by the Federal Election Commission","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"and had received \" unanimous approval \" from it .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Barkan , the progressive activist","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"who created the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and his Be a Hero PAC have selected a nominee fund for the pledges","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"if they become contributions","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that will go toward Collins ' s eventual opponent ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"which ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"is legal .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"In an emailed statement to , Adams-Falconer said","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"the response to the campaign has been \" incredible \"","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"and an example","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"of tens of thousands of people","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"expressing their political speech","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and \" counteracting the dark money","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that has poured in from big , corporate groups \" for years . \"","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"The notion","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that this grassroots activism amounts to bribery","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"is ridiculous and insulting to the more than 40,000 Mainers and other Americans","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"who are making their voice heard through this campaign -","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"no matter which way she votes ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Senator Collins will not receive anything of value from this campaign , \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Despite Crowdpac ' s defense ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"the Wall Street Journal ' s editorial board jumped onto the bribery bandwagon on Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"the campaign is clear \" quid pro quo \"","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"and questioning its legality .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"\" We ' re all for citizens","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"exercising their free-speech rights ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"including campaign donations , for or against political candidates , \"","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"the board wrote .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"\" But federal law defines the crime of bribery as ' corruptly ' offering ' anything of value to a public official ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"including a Member of Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"with the intent","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"to ' influence any official act . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Collins told the Journal","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that three attorneys had told her","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"it ' s a \" clear violation \" of federal law .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"In the same interview , she also complained about \" out-of-state voicemails \"","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"being left on answering machine in her offices .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Activists have also mailed her wire hangers ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"referencing a dangerous abortion method","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"women sometimes resort to","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"when the medical procedure is illegal .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Some progressives have pointed out","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"while many on the right are complaining about the grassroots crowdfunding campaign around Collins as bribery ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"they seem to have no such qualms about campaign donations from major corporations or billionaires such as the Koch brothers ,","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"which are completely legal under campaign finance laws .","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"`` I much prefer to get bribes from the Koch Brothers and other right-wing billionaires , ''","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"@ SenatorCollins continued","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"( probably )","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"https : //t.co/LW2IVfY3","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"re - Tommy Vietor","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"( @ TVietor08 )","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"September 11 , 2018","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"Susan Collins is complaining about citizen participation in democracy .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Not a good look .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"# mepolitics","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"https : //t.co/dfvrPX8DTj","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"- Topher Spiro","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"( @ TopherSpiro )","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"September 11 , 2018","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Small donors matter , @ SenatorCollins .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"I donated $ 20.20 to this @ AdyBarkan campaign","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"not as a method of extortion of bribery .","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"It was to show you","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"just how important # StopKavanaugh is to me .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"Clearly this is important to the 37,690 people","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"who also donated to date .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"- Ellen McCain","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"( @ RespectWomen16 )","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"September 11 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"Collins told Newsmax","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"that the crowdfunding campaign out of Maine would not influence her vote at all","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"and took a swipe at the groups","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"organizing it .","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"\" I think","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"it demonstrates the new lows","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"to which the judge ' s opponents have stooped , \"","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"she said .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"In the same statement , she described the campaign as a \" quid pro quo \"","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"that essentially amounts to a \" bribe . \"","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"It ' s a signal","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"that Collins is feeling the pressure from activists","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"pushing her to vote no on Kavanaugh .","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"But whether it ' s actually a bribe isn ' t really clear .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"As mentioned ,","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"the campaign isn ' t offering to pay her","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"if she votes no -","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"if she does ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"everybody just gets their money back .","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"If she votes yes ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"the money will eventually go to her Democratic challenger ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"but that ' s conceivably not all that different from any other grassroots political campaign .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Beyond Collins , crowdfunding has been on the rise in politics .","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"There are dozens of campaigns","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"listed on the Crowdpac website right now ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"including fundraisers for specific candidates , committees , and causes .","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"One campaign is aimed at helping potential voters get money","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"so they can get identification","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"to vote .","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"Another appears to be run by Arnold Schwarzenegger in an effort","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"to combat gerrymandering .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"\" Basically , anything","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"that ' s in the news right now","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"is getting a tremendous response with social media and crowdfunding , \"","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"Jesse Thomas , the acting CEO of Crowdpac , recently told me .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"\" And the attention is really being monetized . \"","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"Case in point :","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"When I spoke with Thomas late last month ,","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"the Collins-pegged crowdfunding campaign had raised $ 150,000 .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"It ' s now at more than $ 1 million .","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"Multiple figures","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"who have been spurned by President Donald Trump","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"have had success in the crowdfunding realm this year ,","depth":6},{"id":187,"text":"including Stormy Daniels , Andrew McCabe , Peter Strzok , and Michael Cohen .","depth":6},{"id":188,"text":"McCabe , Strzok , and Cohen ran their campaigns on GoFundMe ;","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"Daniels ,","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"whose real name is Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"used CrowdJustice , a fundraising website","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"aimed at raising money for legal matters .","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"In the current environment , many Americans are looking to get involved in the political system any way","depth":5},{"id":194,"text":"they can","depth":5},{"id":195,"text":"-","depth":5},{"id":196,"text":"by voting ,","depth":6},{"id":197,"text":"by protesting ,","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"by calling ,","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"and , yes , by donating their money .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":399,"left":244,"right":398,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":206,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":202,"right":205,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":201,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":3,"right":204,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":4,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":210,"right":242,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":208,"right":209,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":7,"right":207,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":211,"right":241,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":211,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":226,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":214,"right":225,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":212,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":215,"right":224,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":224,"left":20,"right":223,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":223,"left":218,"right":222,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"paren